<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Ella Joy Ignacio — YouTube Growth & Content Operations</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #faf7f2;        /* Soft, creamy milk-tea background */
    --bg-alt: #f3ede2;    /* Slightly darker beige for sections */
    --card: #ffffff;      /* Pure white cards that pop off the cream */
    --border: #e6dcce;    /* Warm, subtle border lines */
    --text: #3d2f28;      /* Soft dark brown text */
    --text-dim: #8c7a6b;  /* Muted taupe for descriptions */
    --accent: #f29da5;    /* Gorgeous aesthetic dusty rose pink */
    --accent-dim: #df848d;/* Darker rose pink for button hovers */
    --accent-ink: #ffffff;/* White text for inside your pink buttons */
  }

  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}
  
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    scroll-padding-top: 80px;
  }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  .wrap { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

  header {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  nav {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px;
    padding: 18px 0;
  }

  .logo {
    font-family: "Didot", "Bodoni MT", Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .logo span { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .nav-cta {
    border: 1px solid var(--accent); color: var(--accent);
    padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent); color: var(--accent-ink); }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }
  .reveal.active {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .hero { padding: 120px 0 100px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .hero-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center; }
  
  .photo-placeholder {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px dashed var(--border); border-radius: 20px;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 13px; text-align: center; padding: 20px;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }
  .photo-placeholder:hover { transform: scale(1.02); }
  .photo-placeholder .ph-icon {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(242, 157, 165, 0.15);
    color: var(--accent); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px;
  }

  .photo-gallery { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-top: 24px; }
  .photo-placeholder.small { aspect-ratio: 1/1; border-radius: 14px; padding: 10px; font-size: 11px; gap: 6px; }
  .photo-placeholder.small .ph-icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; font-size: 15px; }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block; font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 999px;
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: "Didot", "Bodoni MT", Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.05;
    max-width: 820px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  h1 .accent { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; }
  
  .hero p.sub { font-size: 19px; color: var(--text-dim); max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent); color: var(--accent-ink); font-weight: 700;
    padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 15px;
    display: inline-block; transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(242, 157, 165, 0.3);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent-dim); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .btn-secondary {
    border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text); background: var(--card);
    padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 15px;
    display: inline-block; transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .stats {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 64px; padding-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    max-width: 700px;
  }
  .stat-num { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); font-family: Georgia, serif; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 4px; }

  section { padding: 90px 0; }
  .section-tag { font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 600; }
  
  h2 {
    font-family: "Didot", "Bodoni MT", Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  
  .section-intro { color: var(--text-dim); max-width: 600px; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; }

  .about { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg-alt); }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: start; }
  .about p { color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; }
  
  .about-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px; }
  .about-card h3 { font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--text-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; font-weight: 600; }
  
  .quick-info-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-top: 20px; }
  .info-badge-card {
    background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .info-badge-card span.dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; }

  .bullet-cards-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; }
  .bullet-card {
    background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 20px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .bullet-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent-dim); }
  .bullet-card .check-icon { color: var(--accent); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; }

  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; }
  .service-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .service-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(61,47,39,0.02); }
  .service-icon {
    width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(242, 157, 165, 0.15);
    color: var(--accent); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .service-card h3 { font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 700; }
  .service-card p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* HORIZONTAL SCROLL STRUCTURAL STYLES */
  .horizontal-scroll-container {
    position: relative;
    height: 240vh;
    background: var(--bg-alt);
  }
  
  .sticky-wrapper {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
    height: calc(100vh - 80px);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .scroll-track {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    padding: 0 max(24px, calc((100vw - 1080px) / 2));
    width: max-content;
    will-change: transform;
    transition: transform 0.1s linear;
  }

  .case-study {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; gap: 40px; align-items: center;
    width: min(85vw, 920px);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .case-badge {
    display: inline-block; background: rgba(242, 157, 165, 0.15); color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .case-study h3 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .case-study p { color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 15px; }
  
  .case-action-btns { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .case-action-btns .btn-primary, .case-action-btns .btn-secondary { padding: 10px 22px; font-size: 14px; }

  .youtube-preview-card {
    background: #110e0c; border: 1px solid #2d2520; border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16/10; position: relative;
  }
  .yt-thumb-area {
    flex: 1; background: #1a1512; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative;
  }
  .yt-play-btn {
    width: 64px; height: 64px; background: #ff0000; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-size: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,0,0,0.4); transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .youtube-preview-card:hover .yt-play-btn { transform: scale(1.1); }
  .yt-bar {
    background: #1a1512; padding: 14px 20px; border-top: 1px solid #2d2520;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .yt-avatar { width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .yt-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .yt-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; }
  .yt-subtitle { font-size: 12px; color: #a19085; }

  .experience-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px; margin-top: 24px; }
  .exp-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px; padding: 36px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr; gap: 40px; align-items: start; transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .exp-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(61,47,39,0.03); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .exp-meta h3 { font-family: "Didot", "Bodoni MT", Georgia, serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.3; color: var(--text); }
  .exp-desc p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 15.5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  
  .exp-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
  .exp-tags span {
    background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 999px; color: var(--text);
  }

  /* RE-ENGINEERED LOGO-LESS TOOLS STYLING */
  .tools-section { background: var(--bg-alt); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .tool-cat-group { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .tool-cat-group:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .tool-cat-title { font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 18px; font-weight: 700; }
  
  .tools-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(190px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .tool-badge {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 20px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  .tool-badge:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.01); }
  .tool-badge .tool-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .tool-badge span { font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); }

  .cert-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; margin-top: 28px; }
  .cert-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .cert-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .cert-icon-box {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(242, 157, 165, 0.12); border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700;
  }
  .cert-card span { font-weight: 600; font-size: 14.5px; color: var(--text); }

  .process-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 32px; }
  .process-step { border-top: 2px solid var(--accent); padding-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .process-num { font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Georgia, serif; }
  .process-step h3 { font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700; }
  .process-step p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }

  .cta-section { text-align: center; background: var(--bg); padding: 100px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .cta-card { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
  .cta-section h2 { font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 46px); margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.15; }
  .cta-section p { font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-dim); max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto 36px; }

  .contact { background: var(--bg-alt); text-align: center; }
  .contact h2 { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 16px; }
  .contact p { color: var(--text-dim); max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 36px; }
  
  .social-text-links { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 32px; margin-top: 32px; }
  .social-link { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-dim); transition: color 0.2s; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border); padding-bottom: 2px; }
  .social-link:hover { color: var(--accent-dim); border-color: var(--accent-dim); }

  footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 36px 0; text-align: center; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 13.5px; background: var(--bg-alt); }

  @media (max-width: 820px){
    nav { justify-content: center; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    .about-grid, .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .case-study { grid-template-columns: 1fr; width: 85vw; padding: 24px; gap: 24px; }
    .hero-grid .photo-placeholder { order: -1; aspect-ratio: 16/9; }
    .exp-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; padding: 28px; }
    .process-list { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
    .stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .horizontal-scroll-container { height: auto; }
    .sticky-wrapper { position: relative; top: 0; height: auto; overflow: visible; padding: 60px 0; }
    .scroll-track { flex-direction: column; width: 100%; padding: 0 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <nav class="wrap">
    <div class="logo">Ella Joy <span>Ignacio</span></div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#services">Services</a>
      <a href="#work">Work</a>
      <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
      <a href="#process">Process</a>
    </div>
    <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Let's talk</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero reveal">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Social media & YouTube growth</span>
      <h1>I help creators and brands turn content into <span class="accent">consistent growth.</span></h1>
      <p class="sub">Full-service social media management — from scroll-stopping carousels to edited Shorts and thumbnails — so you can focus on the work while your channels keep growing.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Start a project</a>
        <a href="#work" class="btn-secondary">See my work</a>
