          <div class="stat-num">100+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Shorts & carousels produced</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">Full</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Content ops, start to finish</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-placeholder">
      <div class="ph-icon">◎</div>
      <span>Headshot photo goes here</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT Me SECTION -->
<section class="about reveal" id="about">
  <div class="wrap about-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="section-tag">About Me</div>
      <h2>Hi, I’m Ella Joy B. Ignacio</h2>
      <p>I’m a 24-year-old content operations and social media support specialist based in BGC, Philippines. I graduated with a Bachelor of Science in Business Administration major in Management, and I’ve built cross-disciplinary experience across YouTube operations, social media content, admin support, client service, and digital marketing.</p>
      <p>I enjoy working behind the scenes to help creators, founders, and businesses stay consistent online — from editing Shorts and designing thumbnails to uploading blogs, managing content calendars, supporting email campaigns, and keeping structural database workflows meticulously organized.</p>
      
      <div class="photo-gallery">
        <div class="photo-placeholder small"><div class="ph-icon">◎</div><span>Work Sample 1</span></div>
        <div class="photo-placeholder small"><div class="ph-icon">◎</div><span>Work Sample 2</span></div>
        <div class="photo-placeholder small"><div class="ph-icon">◎</div><span>Work Sample 3</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="about-card">
      <h3>Quick Profile</h3>
      <div class="quick-info-grid">
        <div class="info-badge-card"><span class="dot"></span> Based in BGC, Philippines</div>
        <div class="info-badge-card"><span class="dot"></span> BSBA Major in Management</div>
        <div class="info-badge-card"><span class="dot"></span> Content Operations & Support</div>
        <div class="info-badge-card"><span class="dot"></span> Admin, CSR & Logistics Experience</div>
        <div class="info-badge-card"><span class="dot"></span> Remote-friendly setup</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT I BRING TO EVERY PROJECT SECTION -->
<section class="reveal" style="padding: 60px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag">Core Value</div>
    <h2>What I Bring to Every Project</h2>
    <p class="section-intro" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">More than basic tasks, I build systems that clear up your mental bandwidth.</p>
    <div class="bullet-cards-grid">
      <div class="bullet-card"><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Content consistency across major public timelines</div>
      <div class="bullet-card"><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Fast communication and high structural responsiveness</div>
      <div class="bullet-card"><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Organized workflows built to match modern tools</div>
      <div class="bullet-card"><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Strong attention to detail (zero typos or missed rules)</div>
      <div class="bullet-card"><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Creative editing and eye-catching layout support</div>
      <div class="bullet-card"><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Native YouTube algorithm and audience dynamics understanding</div>
      <div class="bullet-card"><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Corporate admin, document filing, and client handling experience</div>
      <div class="bullet-card"><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Lifelong agility to adapt and master new software systems quickly</div>
      <div class="bullet-card"><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Secure, reliable, autonomous remote support ecosystem</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT I CAN HELP YOU WITH SECTION -->
<section id="services" class="reveal">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag">Services</div>
    <h2>What I Can Help You With</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">I help creators, founders, and small teams stay consistent online by handling the content, admin, and digital tasks that take too much time.</p>
    
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">▼</div>
        <h3>YouTube Content Operations</h3>
        <p>Shorts creation, thumbnails, video uploads, titles, descriptions, scheduling, metadata updates, and end-to-end content repurposing assets.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">✂</div>
        <h3>Short-Form Video Editing</h3>
        <p>Turning long-form raw video files into engaging Shorts, TikToks, and Reels configured with punchy hooks, kinetic captions, optimal pacing, and clean aesthetic editing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">▢</div>
        <h3>Thumbnail & Graphic Design</h3>
        <p>Designing clickable high-CTR YouTube thumbnails, clean multi-platform social graphics, and distinct branded assets built in Canva and creative tools.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">▦</div>
        <h3>LinkedIn & Instagram Carousels</h3>
        <p>Creating beautiful, swipeable carousel slides that simplify heavy ideas, educate audiences, and support high-end personal brand authority.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">↥</div>
        <h3>Social Media Management</h3>
        <p>Managing public timelines across Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, and YouTube through hands-off posting, scheduling dashboard deployment, caption copy, and foundational engagement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">⚙</div>
